::Shadow Wing::

She looked at Stegotron. "If you can reallyt fix him up, then let's 
go for it."
She looked at Lunarpine, "this may be the only chance you've got. 
Please go with Stegotron and have him try to fix your eyes. if he is 
successful, you'll see again. And if not, your none the worse for 
wear. You'll have lost nothing. Please gowith him."

She knew it sounded like she was begging.  But she wasn't. She was 
practically grovelling for him to go through with it.  She knew in 
her spark that the Matrix would pull him through this one if he only 
go and do it.
